WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:08.791
[announcer 1] <i>Warning.
Watching this program is mandatory.</i>

00:08.791 --> 00:11.041
<i>Every offender will get a 500-credit fine.</i>

00:12.125 --> 00:14.041
[announcer 2] <i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>

00:14.041 --> 00:18.041
<i>welcome to this very special edition
of</i> The Eden Report<i>.</i>

00:18.041 --> 00:20.041
<i>Retribution Day!</i>

00:20.041 --> 00:24.250
<i>-With your host, Rayman!</i>
- [audience cheering, applauding]

00:24.250 --> 00:26.333
Thank you! Thank you!

00:26.333 --> 00:30.625
You're amazing! You're amazing!
And this day is amazing.

00:30.625 --> 00:31.583
Because it's...

00:31.583 --> 00:33.458
[audience] Retribution Day!

00:33.458 --> 00:36.375
[TV Rayman chuckles]
Yeah. Retribution Day. Yes.

00:36.375 --> 00:38.291
In precisely 30 minutes,

00:38.291 --> 00:44.041
you're gonna witness live
the execution of the terrorist Bullfrog!

00:44.041 --> 00:46.083
[audience cheers, applauding]

00:46.083 --> 00:47.583
[TV Rayman on radio] <i>Yes, yes.</i>

00:47.583 --> 00:52.458
<i>The ruthless assassin responsible
for the Labor District massacre.</i>

00:52.458 --> 00:56.875
<i>Partner in crime of Marcus Holloway
and Dolph Laserhawk.</i>

00:56.875 --> 01:00.291
- [audience booing]
- [showgoer] <i>You fucking suck, asshole!</i>

01:00.291 --> 01:02.333
[TV Rayman] <i>I know, I know.</i>

01:02.333 --> 01:03.791
<i>So before we start the show,</i>

01:03.791 --> 01:08.875
<i>please join me in one minute of silence
in honor of the victims of terrorism.</i>

01:08.875 --> 01:09.791
[Dolph] Huh?

01:09.791 --> 01:13.208
[system AI] <i>Warning. Virus detected.
Warning. Virus detected.</i>

01:13.208 --> 01:15.208
[Dolph groans, screams]

01:20.916 --> 01:25.083
[radio] <i>Take first security precautions
to avoid becoming the victim of an attack.</i>

01:25.916 --> 01:28.208
[radio chatter continues]

01:28.208 --> 01:31.791
- [Dolph groans, breathing heavily]
- [electricity crackling]

01:32.375 --> 01:33.583
What is happening to me?

01:33.583 --> 01:37.666
[system AI] <i>Trojan infection
in progress. 25% and rising.</i>

01:37.666 --> 01:39.750
Locate the source of infection.

01:40.333 --> 01:41.958
[system AI] <i>Source of infection...</i>

01:42.541 --> 01:44.250
<i>Port B.24, left arm.</i>

01:44.250 --> 01:45.166
[Dolph] What?

01:46.333 --> 01:47.166
[gasps]

01:48.958 --> 01:49.833
No.

01:49.833 --> 01:51.416
[system AI] <i>Time of infection...</i>

01:52.083 --> 01:55.666
- [Dolph] No.
- [system AI] <i>0846, today.</i>

01:55.666 --> 01:58.500
[tense darksynth music playing]

02:02.958 --> 02:06.708
I'm very pleased to announce,
dear citizens of Eden,

02:06.708 --> 02:09.916
that this execution
is just the first step.

02:09.916 --> 02:11.208
[Dolph grunting]

02:11.208 --> 02:14.208
[TV Rayman on radio] <i>You know
that today is Retribution Day, right?</i>

02:14.208 --> 02:17.583
Well, here's a big surprise for you.

02:17.583 --> 02:21.458
<i>At this moment,
the Niji 6 and our brave soldiers</i>

02:21.458 --> 02:26.375
<i>are on their way to deliver
the final blow to these monsters!</i>

02:26.375 --> 02:28.458
- [audience cheering]
- Fisher!

02:28.458 --> 02:30.166
Yes! Yes!

02:30.166 --> 02:34.416
So stay with us, because we have
the most amazing show tonight.

02:34.416 --> 02:36.250
See you after the break.

02:36.250 --> 02:39.125
[music crescendos, ends]

02:46.166 --> 02:51.583
[darksynth theme music playing]

03:00.083 --> 03:01.083
[music ends]

03:06.875 --> 03:08.166
[Marcus panting]

03:09.375 --> 03:11.291
I should've listened to my gut.

03:12.166 --> 03:15.083
You're still the same
brainwashed little brat.

03:15.083 --> 03:18.291
You really got me good.
You and your cyber slave.

03:18.791 --> 03:21.375
No, no.
Laserhawk has nothing to do with this.

03:22.000 --> 03:25.375
I just needed him
to infect your precious VR facility.

03:25.375 --> 03:28.041
Unfortunately,
his body won't survive the virus.

03:28.708 --> 03:32.875
But on the bright side, this place
will be in my control in no time.

03:33.750 --> 03:34.833
Hmm?

03:34.833 --> 03:37.333
[mechanical droning]

03:41.416 --> 03:43.583
[guns priming]

03:43.583 --> 03:45.958
[chuckles] Oh, Marcus.

03:45.958 --> 03:47.916
It's cute, but unnecessary.

03:47.916 --> 03:49.166
[Marcus panting]

03:50.541 --> 03:52.875
[Sarah] Marcus, the reason
you're still breathing right now

03:52.875 --> 03:54.625
is because I want it that way.

03:56.041 --> 03:57.666
I've got an offer for you.

03:59.375 --> 04:01.458
Go fuck yourself, Little Sarah.

04:02.166 --> 04:04.208
[tense darksynth music playing]

04:04.208 --> 04:05.291
[Sarah chuckles]

04:13.916 --> 04:15.875
Okay. You wanna play?

04:17.291 --> 04:18.875
Let's play, then.

04:24.500 --> 04:27.958
It seems you've forgotten something,
you Eden scum.

04:27.958 --> 04:32.250
You may be the best at lying and cheating,
but I'm the best at what I do.

04:37.250 --> 04:40.750
<i>Say goodbye
to your stupid-ass virus, asshole.</i>

04:43.125 --> 04:45.791
[music fades]

04:45.791 --> 04:47.875
[blues rock music playing]

04:52.125 --> 04:54.375
- [diners chattering]
- [porcelain clinks]

04:55.458 --> 04:56.958
[music continues, muffled]

04:56.958 --> 04:58.458
[zipper opens]

05:00.333 --> 05:03.541
I am... I'm not sure about this.

05:03.541 --> 05:05.541
[Rayman] It's the only way, man.

05:05.541 --> 05:08.958
But the Board of Directors
has always been fair to us.

05:08.958 --> 05:11.291
I'm-- I'm sure they can be reasonable.

05:11.291 --> 05:13.750
We've been replaced. You hear me?

05:13.750 --> 05:15.416
I don't know how, but they did it.

05:15.416 --> 05:18.958
They sent the fucking Niji 6
because we represent a risk for 'em.

05:18.958 --> 05:19.875
Do you understand me?

05:19.875 --> 05:22.500
But... I want our old life back.

05:22.500 --> 05:23.958
[Rayman] "Our life"?

05:23.958 --> 05:28.333
You wanna look away and spread their lies
with a dumb smile on your face?

05:29.458 --> 05:30.458
No.

05:31.250 --> 05:33.083
I can't look away anymore.

05:33.083 --> 05:37.250
They're gonna slaughter
another innocent hybrid live on <i>my</i> show,

05:37.250 --> 05:38.500
with <i>my</i> face!

05:40.333 --> 05:42.208
I won't allow that.

05:42.208 --> 05:43.750
Maybe we can beg.

05:43.750 --> 05:47.291
Come on! Let's beg for mercy.
We're pretty good at that, right?

05:47.291 --> 05:48.708
- [Rayman grunts]
- [gunfire]

05:48.708 --> 05:50.791
[imposing rock music playing]

05:51.750 --> 05:53.875
Those days are over.

05:56.458 --> 05:59.125
- [diner door bell chiming]
- [door closes]

06:00.125 --> 06:02.458
Now it's time for Eden to meet...

06:03.125 --> 06:04.583
Ramon.

06:05.208 --> 06:09.958
[music continues]

06:09.958 --> 06:11.791
[Sergeant] <i>Listen up, people!</i>

06:11.791 --> 06:14.541
Today is a glorious day for Eden.

06:14.541 --> 06:17.500
We're taking back the VR
from those goddamn rebels.

06:17.500 --> 06:21.750
If they oppose any resistance,
I want you to shoot them on sight.

06:22.333 --> 06:23.541
[Red] "Resistance"? Really?

06:23.541 --> 06:26.291
A-A five-year-old could take down
these fucking zombies.

06:26.291 --> 06:27.625
[Violet laughs]

06:27.625 --> 06:30.458
You said the same thing
about taking care of Rayman,

06:30.458 --> 06:31.958
and yet he's still on the run.

06:31.958 --> 06:33.875
[Red] Shut the fuck up! You weren't there!

06:33.875 --> 06:36.125
[Violet] Yeah, I know.
Because if I was there, he--

06:36.125 --> 06:39.041
[Yellow] Guys, guys, wait.
I got something on the radar.

06:43.041 --> 06:44.583
[Red] Ooh.

06:47.583 --> 06:49.875
Huh? What the fuck are you doing?!

06:59.791 --> 07:03.833
[Red] Aw, look at that little baby hawk
falling out of the nest.

07:04.416 --> 07:07.916
What a shame.
It pains me to see you in this state.

07:08.458 --> 07:09.583
Let me...

07:11.250 --> 07:12.583
give you a hand.

07:12.583 --> 07:13.500
[Sergeant] Red!

07:16.875 --> 07:20.041
The orders are to go
straight to the VR facility.

07:20.041 --> 07:23.458
The Directors said
that Laserhawk is no longer a threat.

07:23.458 --> 07:26.291
I mean, look at him!
He can barely stand on his--

07:26.291 --> 07:27.333
[gasps] Oh boy.

07:27.333 --> 07:29.500
- [explosion]
- [Sergeant screaming]

07:29.500 --> 07:30.458
[groaning]

07:31.125 --> 07:33.708
[system AI] <i>Warning.
Plasma capacity unstable. Warning.</i>

07:33.708 --> 07:37.250
- [Dolph yells]
- [cannon firing]

07:37.250 --> 07:39.416
[system AI] <i>Warning. Warning. Warning.</i>

07:39.416 --> 07:41.000
[Dolph screams, groans]

07:41.000 --> 07:43.083
What-- what are you waiting for?

07:43.083 --> 07:44.041
Fire!

07:44.041 --> 07:45.500
- [Red] No!
- [Sergeant] What?

07:49.583 --> 07:50.583
[Red] He's mine!

07:52.583 --> 07:54.166
Come and get some,

07:55.291 --> 07:56.708
Laserfuck!

08:03.666 --> 08:07.250
Hmm. You know what, Fisher?
This is a tough one to crack.

08:08.750 --> 08:10.750
Whoever created that virus is...

08:11.541 --> 08:13.333
pretty good, I must say.

08:14.041 --> 08:16.833
But... not good enough.

08:16.833 --> 08:17.833
[metal clangs]

08:17.833 --> 08:18.875
[Marcus] Hmm?

08:24.250 --> 08:25.708
- [Sarah grunts]
- [metal bangs]

08:26.416 --> 08:28.958
Open that door, Holloway.

08:28.958 --> 08:30.875
[scoffs] Or what?

08:30.875 --> 08:32.291
You're gonna huff and puff--

08:32.291 --> 08:34.583
[Sarah on speakers]
<i>You still think this is a game, right?</i>

08:35.958 --> 08:36.833
[Marcus] Huh?

08:37.583 --> 08:38.708
Where the fuck is she?

08:43.875 --> 08:46.291
- Fisher, what are you doing?
- [Sarah] <i>Well...</i>

08:47.125 --> 08:49.458
The difference between you and me, Marcus...

08:50.583 --> 08:52.000
[Marcus on speakers] <i>Fisher.</i>

08:53.791 --> 08:55.333
...is that I'm not playing.

08:55.333 --> 08:56.500
[Marcus] <i>No. No, no, no.</i>

08:56.500 --> 08:57.750
No!

09:00.041 --> 09:01.208
<i>No!</i>

09:04.458 --> 09:06.666
You fucking monster!

09:06.666 --> 09:09.083
[Sarah] <i>So this is
what's gonna happen, Marcus.</i>

09:10.125 --> 09:14.333
You're gonna let the virus do its thing,
and you're gonna open that door.

09:15.416 --> 09:16.750
It's your choice.

09:21.541 --> 09:24.166
You fucking asshole.

09:24.166 --> 09:26.833
[Sarah] Oh.
That's your friend T-Bone, right?

09:28.166 --> 09:30.333
I didn't know
he survived the Wasteland War.

09:32.291 --> 09:33.458
Oh well.

09:34.208 --> 09:35.458
[Marcus] <i>Stop!</i>

09:35.458 --> 09:39.375
[blast doors opening]

09:43.958 --> 09:45.958
[Marcus breathing heavily]

09:45.958 --> 09:46.875
[Sarah] So...

09:49.208 --> 09:50.333
About that offer.

09:51.333 --> 09:54.375
- [Dolph grunts, groaning]
- [Red laughs]

09:54.375 --> 09:56.083
This is awesome!

09:56.083 --> 09:57.750
- Whoo!
- [Dolph grunts]

10:00.083 --> 10:01.958
- [Red] Are you tired yet?
- [Dolph gasps]

10:01.958 --> 10:02.875
[groans]

10:03.583 --> 10:05.375
[ringing in ears]

10:05.375 --> 10:07.166
[Dolph groaning]

10:08.458 --> 10:11.375
[breathing heavily]

10:11.375 --> 10:15.125
[mechanical footsteps approaching]

10:15.125 --> 10:19.833
[Red] Well, I hope
it was as fun for you as it was for me.

10:19.833 --> 10:23.791
But all good things
must come to an end, eventually.

10:24.500 --> 10:28.375
So, it's time we say goodbye, Captain.

10:28.375 --> 10:30.166
- And--
- [ad] <i>See the world like a champion.</i>

10:30.166 --> 10:31.166
[Red] Oh. Hold on.

10:32.333 --> 10:33.500
Right on time.

10:34.166 --> 10:35.666
<i>Yeah, what are you gonna do?</i>

10:35.666 --> 10:36.708
[chuckles]

10:36.708 --> 10:41.791
Okay. We are now mere seconds away
from tonight's big event.

10:41.791 --> 10:43.875
<i>Are you guys ready?</i>

10:43.875 --> 10:46.500
- [audience applauding]
- [TV Rayman] <i>So, Mr. Bullfrog.</i>

10:46.500 --> 10:48.833
You thought you could kill innocent people

10:48.833 --> 10:51.791
and threaten Eden's way of life
and get away with it?

10:51.791 --> 10:52.916
[audience booing]

10:52.916 --> 10:54.666
[chuckles] Too bad.

10:54.666 --> 10:55.833
[audience applauding]

10:55.833 --> 10:58.333
[TV Rayman] <i>Before we proceed
with the execution,</i>

10:59.041 --> 11:02.250
<i>I've got one last
very important question for you.</i>

11:02.250 --> 11:04.833
And think about it very carefully,

11:04.833 --> 11:09.208
because these are gonna be
your last words!

11:09.208 --> 11:13.875
- [game show musical interlude plays]
- [audience cheering, applauding]

11:13.875 --> 11:16.750
- So here's my question.
- [suspenseful quiz show music playing]

11:16.750 --> 11:21.708
And there's nothing for you to win,
except maybe the redemption of your soul.

11:21.708 --> 11:23.125
Mr. Bullfrog,

11:24.250 --> 11:28.708
when you think about what you did,
do you have any regrets?

11:32.791 --> 11:33.625
I...

11:35.750 --> 11:38.666
As a matter of fact, I do have regrets.

11:38.666 --> 11:39.583
Ooh.

11:41.833 --> 11:44.791
I have blood on my hands, yes. Of course.

11:45.750 --> 11:47.916
I followed the path of the <i>assassin</i>,

11:48.666 --> 11:50.250
but this path has a code.

11:50.833 --> 11:51.875
A code of honor.

11:52.875 --> 11:55.541
So that, I don't regret.

11:56.666 --> 11:57.500
No.

11:58.708 --> 12:01.500
I'm sorry for my comrades.

12:02.458 --> 12:03.291
Jade,

12:04.208 --> 12:05.333
Pey'j,

12:05.333 --> 12:07.541
and even that stupid Cody Rhodes.

12:08.833 --> 12:11.500
Hmm. I should have been there for them.

12:12.708 --> 12:15.125
These are my regrets.

12:16.833 --> 12:21.750
Capitaine <i>Dolph Laserhawk,
I hope you're still alive somewhere.</i>

12:22.250 --> 12:23.083
<i>I...</i>

12:23.791 --> 12:25.041
<i>I failed you.</i>

12:26.875 --> 12:27.708
<i>Je...</i>

12:28.833 --> 12:30.916
<i>Je suis désolé, mon ami.</i>

12:32.333 --> 12:33.833
[audience booing]

12:33.833 --> 12:37.125
I know, I know. I'm as angry as you are.

12:37.791 --> 12:38.958
But don't worry.

12:38.958 --> 12:41.125
He's now facing his fate

12:41.125 --> 12:43.625
and will answer for what he has done.

12:44.750 --> 12:46.416
Right after the break!

12:46.416 --> 12:47.666
[musical interlude plays]

12:47.666 --> 12:48.625
[Red groans]

12:48.625 --> 12:51.041
Fuck these commercials! Really?

12:51.041 --> 12:52.583
Okay, okay.

12:52.583 --> 12:54.083
You know what, Laserhawk?

12:54.083 --> 12:55.958
Let's cut to the fucking chase.

12:58.583 --> 13:00.041
Good night.

13:00.708 --> 13:02.000
[ground slams]

13:02.000 --> 13:03.083
Whoa!

13:03.083 --> 13:05.583
Fuck yeah! Damn, that felt good!

13:05.583 --> 13:06.875
- [alarm blaring]
- [Red whimpers]

13:06.875 --> 13:09.125
- [alarm] <i>Warning. Warning. Warning.</i>
- [Red] What the fuck?

13:09.708 --> 13:10.708
[low rumbling]

13:10.708 --> 13:12.125
Oh shit.

13:12.125 --> 13:13.333
Oh, not again.

13:13.333 --> 13:17.500
[Dolph] First, I'm gonna kick
your red baboon ass.

13:18.083 --> 13:22.083
Second, I'm gonna kick
that double-crossing bitch's ass.

13:22.083 --> 13:23.875
- [metal creaks]
- [Red groans]

13:24.458 --> 13:26.916
[Dolph] And then, and only then,

13:27.833 --> 13:29.625
I will die!

13:29.625 --> 13:31.833
["Turbo Killer" by Carpenter Brut playing]

13:31.833 --> 13:33.958
[Niji 6 screaming]

13:41.208 --> 13:42.375
Bring it on!

13:44.250 --> 13:45.791
[Red] You motherfucker!

13:49.625 --> 13:50.541
[Dolph roars]

13:50.541 --> 13:51.458
[Niji 6 groan]

13:56.291 --> 13:57.833
Holy Mother of God!

13:58.333 --> 13:59.666
Fire!

14:02.708 --> 14:06.166
[Dolph grunting]

14:17.875 --> 14:19.208
[gunfire continues]

14:21.333 --> 14:24.208
- [system AI] <i>Warning. Warning. Warning.</i>
- [Dolph groans, screams]

14:24.208 --> 14:25.375
[music continues]

14:25.375 --> 14:26.291
[Dolph grunting]

14:28.250 --> 14:30.916
[system AI] <i>Warning.
Plasma capacity unstable.</i>

14:30.916 --> 14:33.625
<i>Warning. Warning. Warning. Warning.</i>

14:34.166 --> 14:35.791
[Dolph roars]

14:39.541 --> 14:41.250
[yelling]

14:44.375 --> 14:45.375
[music ends]

14:54.458 --> 14:56.250
- [audience cheering]
- [talk-show music playing]

14:56.250 --> 14:57.791
[Rayman scatting to music]

14:57.791 --> 14:59.958
And we're back! [chuckles]

14:59.958 --> 15:01.958
Ladies and gentlemen, this is it.

15:01.958 --> 15:04.583
This is the moment
you've all been waiting for.

15:04.583 --> 15:07.625
In precisely one minute and 35 seconds,

15:07.625 --> 15:10.875
Bullfrog, the ruthless terrorist,
will receive 40,000 volts...

15:10.875 --> 15:13.333
[Director Alpha] Perfect.
We're on schedule.

15:13.333 --> 15:15.541
Sigma's plan is falling into place.

15:15.541 --> 15:18.208
Laserhawk is probably dead as we speak.

15:18.875 --> 15:22.833
After tonight's execution,
all the Ghosts will be terminated,

15:22.833 --> 15:24.625
and the VR facility will be...

15:27.375 --> 15:29.208
Excuse me. Director Alpha,

15:29.208 --> 15:31.791
I think we have a problem
on the Wasteland frontline.

15:31.791 --> 15:32.708
[Alpha] Uh-huh?

15:33.291 --> 15:35.291
- Sergeant. What is the--
- [Sergeant yelling on phone]

15:35.291 --> 15:38.000
[Alpha] Okay, slow down.
Slow down. I can't hear you.

15:39.000 --> 15:39.833
What?

15:40.541 --> 15:43.958
Sergeant, are you telling me
that one broken cyber terrorist

15:43.958 --> 15:46.375
is taking down an entire army?

15:46.375 --> 15:48.125
Because if that's the case,

15:48.125 --> 15:51.666
you'll be the one sitting in the jail
live on television next week.

15:51.666 --> 15:55.000
- Do I make myself clear? Fix this.
- [phone beeps]

15:55.000 --> 15:57.458
- [Omega] Should we send backup?
- [Alpha] Backup?

15:58.041 --> 16:00.666
What backup? We sent everyone there.

16:07.375 --> 16:08.208
[guard] Huh?

16:11.333 --> 16:13.041
Hey! You!

16:13.041 --> 16:15.625
It's a restricted area.
Hands where I can see them.

16:17.083 --> 16:18.916
Hands? Sure.

16:20.125 --> 16:22.708
Slowly. Slowly.

16:24.208 --> 16:26.125
Aw. Where did you go?

16:26.125 --> 16:27.375
Huh? What?

16:27.375 --> 16:28.291
[groans]

16:28.833 --> 16:32.416
[imposing rock music playing]

16:32.416 --> 16:34.833
Aw. There you are.

16:34.833 --> 16:37.625
That's a very naughty hand.

16:37.625 --> 16:39.375
How about a big round of applause

16:39.375 --> 16:43.083
for the Rayman Kid
that's gonna pull that lever!

16:43.083 --> 16:45.958
<i>Delphine!</i> [chuckles] <i>So cute.</i>

16:46.625 --> 16:50.750
<i>Is everybody ready
for the countdown for justice?</i>

16:52.333 --> 16:53.791
- [Pi] What? Rayman?
- [gunshot]

16:54.333 --> 16:56.458
- [Directors] Huh?
- [Alpha] What's the matter with you?

16:56.458 --> 16:57.750
Nobody makes a fucking move.

16:58.333 --> 16:59.958
Sit the fuck down.

16:59.958 --> 17:01.125
[Alpha] Rayman?

17:01.125 --> 17:03.833
Sit the fuck down!

17:05.500 --> 17:08.083
[Alpha] Okay. Okay. We're sitting down.

17:09.333 --> 17:10.958
[Omega] You know, we understand what you--

17:10.958 --> 17:13.250
[Ramon] I got no time for your bullshit.

17:13.250 --> 17:14.333
The execution.

17:15.541 --> 17:16.541
Call it off.

17:17.458 --> 17:18.291
Now.

17:18.291 --> 17:21.166
[Omega] Rayman,
you know that's impossible.

17:23.875 --> 17:26.083
I don't think
you understand the shit you're in.

17:26.833 --> 17:28.375
This is your last chance.

17:29.000 --> 17:30.458
<i>Come on, everybody.</i>

17:30.458 --> 17:32.541
<i>- Count with me!</i>
- [Ramon] Cut it off.

17:32.541 --> 17:33.541
Now.

17:33.541 --> 17:36.083
[TV Rayman with audience] <i>Ten, nine...</i>

17:36.083 --> 17:40.208
[Omega] Director speaking.
Call the execution off. Right now.

17:40.208 --> 17:41.541
You don't have much time.

17:41.541 --> 17:44.250
[Omega] I don't care!
We will deal with that later!

17:45.208 --> 17:46.500
Cut it off, goddamn it!

17:46.500 --> 17:48.458
- Wait!
- [audience gasps]

17:49.083 --> 17:49.916
What?

17:50.500 --> 17:51.958
Yeah. Uh-huh.

17:52.875 --> 17:53.916
[clears throat]

17:53.916 --> 17:57.916
Okay. It-- it seems that we have
a small technical issue with the chair,

17:57.916 --> 18:00.916
so for safety reasons, we have to, um...

18:00.916 --> 18:02.375
[off-air tone]

18:06.000 --> 18:08.500
[Omega] Okay. Are you happy now?

18:09.125 --> 18:10.541
You have what you wanted.

18:12.125 --> 18:14.791
[Ramon laughing]

18:14.791 --> 18:15.875
Am I happy?

18:16.750 --> 18:17.875
Oh, no.

18:18.875 --> 18:20.208
No, I'm not.

18:24.666 --> 18:27.333
We really have to rearrange
the whole place.

18:27.875 --> 18:30.625
I'm thinking... light blue?

18:30.625 --> 18:35.375
[Marcus] I'm glad that Sam never saw
what you let yourself become.

18:35.375 --> 18:38.375
[Sarah] Oh, yes.
And what about what you've become?

18:38.375 --> 18:40.583
"The Wasteland King." Really? [chuckles]

18:40.583 --> 18:43.291
Is this shadow of a life
all you had to offer them?

18:44.958 --> 18:47.291
It's better than living in your world.

18:47.291 --> 18:49.500
Oh, you're gonna be surprised,
Marcus, but...

18:50.416 --> 18:51.708
I agree with you.

18:51.708 --> 18:53.416
I don't like this world either.

18:55.000 --> 18:58.625
You know, Eden Tech
has gone by many names over time.

18:58.625 --> 19:00.750
You probably heard of the Templar Order?

19:01.541 --> 19:04.166
But they've always been governed
by the same council.

19:04.791 --> 19:08.166
The council
that's grown weak and complacent.

19:09.125 --> 19:10.500
We need new blood.

19:11.458 --> 19:14.416
That's why I'm talking to you right now.

19:14.916 --> 19:17.000
[Marcus chuckles] You can't be serious.

19:18.291 --> 19:22.250
I'm offering you
what everybody lost, even you.

19:22.250 --> 19:24.416
A vision. A path.

19:24.416 --> 19:28.208
If you hate Eden so much,
then help it change.

19:30.541 --> 19:32.625
Who the hell are you?

19:33.916 --> 19:34.750
I'm--

19:34.750 --> 19:38.416
[Dolph] The biggest piece of shit
I've ever met.

19:39.500 --> 19:42.708
[grunting, breathing heavily]

19:42.708 --> 19:45.166
And God knows I've had my share.

19:45.166 --> 19:46.750
[epic darksynth music playing]

19:46.750 --> 19:48.166
Oh my God.

19:48.875 --> 19:52.000
Seems like
you're in a lot of pain, Laserhawk.

19:52.000 --> 19:54.750
Yeah? Then you should see the other guys.

19:55.416 --> 19:56.875
- What?
- [Dolph] Yeah.

19:57.458 --> 19:58.750
About their army...

19:58.750 --> 20:01.375
[clicks tongue]
They won't be joining us after all.

20:02.250 --> 20:05.583
[Sarah laughing]

20:06.208 --> 20:07.708
[Dolph coughs]

20:12.416 --> 20:14.000
Oh, Dolph.

20:14.000 --> 20:15.458
Can I call you Dolph?

20:15.458 --> 20:17.166
[Dolph chuckles] No.

20:18.875 --> 20:19.875
[Warden] Okay.

20:20.625 --> 20:24.000
You are a tough son of a bitch,
Captain Laserhawk, I give you that.

20:25.500 --> 20:28.458
But in the end,
it won't make any difference.

20:28.458 --> 20:30.625
[Dolph coughing, wheezing]

20:30.625 --> 20:32.375
[music fades]

20:35.166 --> 20:37.291
Shh-shh-shh. It's okay.

20:38.666 --> 20:40.208
Just look on the bright side.

20:41.375 --> 20:43.000
You finally got what you wanted.

20:45.083 --> 20:47.583
- Hey, Warden.
- [Sarah] Hmm?

20:49.125 --> 20:49.958
Beep.

20:49.958 --> 20:51.166
- [wrist beeps]
- [Sarah gasps]

20:57.000 --> 21:00.541
["You" by Alex Condliffe playing]

21:05.000 --> 21:10.541
<i>♪ I've got a poison in my veins ♪</i>

21:12.833 --> 21:18.833
<i>♪ Trying to let it all run out ♪</i>

21:20.458 --> 21:25.958
<i>♪ But this river won't run dry ♪</i>

21:28.916 --> 21:34.125
<i>♪ You are the void I cannot fill ♪</i>

21:35.125 --> 21:40.291
[Marcus panting]

21:43.666 --> 21:45.458
- [metal clanging]
- [Marcus] Huh?

21:45.458 --> 21:48.041
[Sarah] I'm very sorry
for the little interruption.

21:50.833 --> 21:51.958
It won't happen again.

21:54.375 --> 21:55.750
So, Marcus.

21:57.291 --> 21:58.291
Are you in?

21:58.958 --> 22:00.750
Or are you out?

22:00.750 --> 22:07.041
[tense darksynth music playing]

22:12.000 --> 22:13.416
[music fading]

22:57.916 --> 22:59.833
[music resumes]
